			<h3>Published <time>17 August 2022</time> in <a href="https://mariothomas.com/categories/aws/">AWS</a>  | 5 minute read | <a href="/blog/cfo/"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/link.svg" alt="Permalink" /></a></h3>
		</header>

		
		<p>CFO Magazine in The Netherlands interviewed me today on the role of the CFO in any cloud transformation. You can <a href="https://cfo.nl/artikel/de-cfo-is-onmisbaar-in-de-cloudtransformatie">read the article here in Dutch</a>.</p>
		
